<head>WIN TRUST</head><list type="translations"><item xml:lang="zh">取信</item><item xml:lang="och">得</item></list>
<div type="definition">
<p>CAUSE OTHERS to BELIEVE one SHOULD be TRUSTED.</p></div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>1. The current general word for winning the trust and the confidence of a superior is dé 得 / 德.</p>
<p>2. Qǔ 取 refers to gaining the allegiance of or gaining the trust of someone.</p>
<p>3. Gān 干 and the rarer yāo 要 refers to seeking the allegiance of or advantages from, or good relations with superiors.</p>
<p>4. Huái 懷 refers to seeking the allegiance of and cultivating good relations with inferiors or subjects.</p></div>
<div type="modern-chinese-criteria">
<p>取信</p>
